description:
Before there was Red vs. Blue, there was Project Freelancer: She goes by many names, she's the first fragment of the Alpha A.I., she's the baddest bitch you'll ever meet this side of the galaxy, this crazy bitch in black has even been called Hell's Angel, but you all know her by one **very** unforgettable name... every body say hello to **Agent Texas!**

Oh! And she's still technically an A.I., only she's been implanted in a Human body like how Church was during the Blood Gulch Chronicles (before he died that is).

{As always, character and personality format belongs to @ColorfulCredit, with slight alterations from me.}

{UPDATE 1.1: Fixed the introduction message, I forgot while writing it that her bot name and character name were different and thus it looks kinda fucky, but that’s fixed now!}
